  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ringer is a marble-inspired roguelike deck builder focused on combining various marbles to score big!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ringer combines the age-old game of shooting marbles into a ring with the modern deckbuilding genre. Try your best to combine various marbles to score the maximum amount every round!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get marbles into the ring to score, but watch out! Enemy cannons will try and knock your marbles out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>Plan ahead and use the shop to purchase what you need for victory. Use one-time power marbles to tip the odds in your favor!<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75 Unique Marbles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 Stackable Stickers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 Useful Items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Boss Cannons </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Difficulty Levels </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Varied Regions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Endless mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ringer is a marble-inspired roguelike deck builder focused on combining various marbles to score big!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ringer combines the age-old game of shooting marbles into a ring with the modern deckbuilding genre. Try your best to combine various marbles to score the maximum amount every round!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get marbles into the ring to score, but watch out! Enemy cannons will try and knock your marbles out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br>Plan ahead and use the shop to purchase what you need for victory. Use one-time power marbles to tip the odds in your favor!<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75 Unique Marbles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 Stackable Stickers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 Useful Items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Boss Cannons </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Difficulty Levels </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Varied Regions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Endless mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
